Description:
In the desert you come across a mysterious dusty lamp. The lamp seems to have something written on it, but you can't see it because of the accumulated dust.

When you rub the lamp, a smiling Djinn suddenly appears out of it. He greets you saying:

"Thank you very much travelers! It's been a long time since I've seen anyone or breathed fresh air, hahaha... I guess, as is the old custom, I should grant you three wishes. Since there are four of you, I'll grant you one wish that works for all of you."
DescriptionAction: What wish would you like to make?
